   da Silva, Zeneide Damiao; Vieira, Thiago Bernardi, Univ Fed Para, Programa Posgrad Zool, Campus Belem, Belem, PA, Brazil.
   Gurgel, Ely Simone Cajueiro, Museu Paraense Emilio Goeldi, Programa Posgrad Ciencias Biol, Bot Trop, Belem, PA, Brazil.
